    },
    "After receiving the signal to fire, quickly **flick your phone upwards**. Raising your whole arm or flicking up your wrist work as long as the **top or bottom** side of your phone is pointing towards the opponent." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "id" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Setelah menerima sinyal untuk menembak, segera **sentakkan ponselmu ke atas**. Mengangkat seluruh lengan maupun menyentakkan pergelangan tangan sama-sama berfungsi selama **sisi atas atau bawah** ponselmu mengarah ke lawan."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Back to Menu" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "id" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Kembali ke Menu"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Before pressing **“Ready,”** take a distance between you and the other player. While this is not required for gameplay, it is advised to **avoid physical** contact with the other player." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "id" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Sebelum menekan **\"Siap,\"** jaga jarak antara kamu dan pemain lain. Meskipun tidak wajib untuk bermain, disarankan untuk **menghindari kontak fisik** dengan pemain lain."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Connection Lost" : {
      "comment" : "A title for a screen that appears when the connection to an opponent is lost.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "id" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Jaringan Hilang"
